descriptionHtml:
This is my first mod for Skyrim. Intended to be fun and scary. Use your wits to get through the Butt Scary Maze, avoid the giant scary monsters, and have fun and play it with friends... or alone... in the dark. Dungeon is found on the cliff side of the city of Whiterun. Once your in, you have to find the key to your freedom. Locate the bag of torches and the journal in the first room to provide you directions on how to escape.

Also I have a gaming channel on youtube. My name is Mr SHABOOSKI!!! I recently uploaded a gameplay for this. Its atÂ https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZM4MsGUS6Bs

I also had another youtuber make a video of his gameplay. His name is Galider 12. Here are the links for his gameplays:

Part 1 : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HAqtnbSuqBU
